      <title>特朗普大选后美国国债有望创下两个月来最佳一周表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/treasuries-set-for-best-week-in-two-months-after-trump-whiplash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统大选胜利的影响，美国国债在过去五个交易日波动较大，本周有望创下自 9 月初以来的最佳表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/treasuries-set-for-best-week-in-two-months-after-trump-whiplash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行暗示鸽派政策决心增强，流动性充裕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/pboc-signals-greater-resolve-on-dovish-policy-ample-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继出台旨在降低地方债务风险的大规模财政刺激计划后，中国央行加强了对支持性货币政策的决心，并承诺使用多种工具确保市场流动性充裕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/pboc-signals-greater-resolve-on-dovish-policy-ample-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:26:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊坎企业减半股息以增持 CVR 能源股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/icahn-enterprises-halves-dividend-to-boost-cvr-energy-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁激进投资者卡尔·伊坎 (Carl Icahn) 的投资基金将把股息削减一半，因为其计划增持 CVR Energy Inc. 的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/icahn-enterprises-halves-dividend-to-boost-cvr-energy-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最大银行利润率收紧导致 SBI 股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/sbi-beats-profit-estimate-on-increased-lending-lower-provisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度国家银行 (State Bank of India) 股价下跌，此前该国最大的银行报告利润率下降，不良贷款拨备增加。该银行预测本财年的存款增长低于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/sbi-beats-profit-estimate-on-increased-lending-lower-provisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国推出 1.4 万亿美元债务互换计划，为特朗普节省刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-unveils-839-billion-debt-swap-to-rescue-local-governments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向负债累累的地方政府提供了 10 万亿元人民币（1.4 万亿美元）的救助金，但没有推出新的刺激措施，为应对唐纳德·特朗普明年上任时可能爆发的贸易战保留空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/china-unveils-839-billion-debt-swap-to-rescue-local-governments</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
